            <rights>[CC BY-NC-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/deed.en)</rights><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Recently, I&amp;rsquo;ve met some software companies where, even in the very early stages with fewer than 8 in the only backend team, they have opted to separate the functions of infrastructure from the general development.&lt;/p&gt;
